@using R_BlazorFrontEnd.Interfaces
@inherits R_Page
@attribute [R_Page(Title = "Copy From Process")];
@inject R_ILocalizer<GSM05000FrontResources_FMC.Resources_Dummy_Class> _localizer

<R_StackLayout Style="width: 800px">
    <R_StackLayout Row Spacing="2" Class="mb-1">
        <R_ItemLayout col="2">
            <R_Label>@_localizer["LABEL_DEPARTMENT"]</R_Label>
        </R_ItemLayout>
        <R_ItemLayout col="2">
            <R_TextBox @bind-Value="@_deptViewModel.ToDept.CDEPT_CODE" Enabled="false" />
        </R_ItemLayout>
        <R_ItemLayout col="7">
            <R_TextBox @bind-Value="@_deptViewModel.ToDept.CDEPT_NAME" Enabled="false" />
        </R_ItemLayout>
    </R_StackLayout>

    <R_StackLayout Row Spacing="2" Class="mb-3">
        <R_ItemLayout col="2">
            <R_Label>@_localizer["LABEL_COPYFROM"]</R_Label>
        </R_ItemLayout>
        <R_ItemLayout col="2">
            <R_TextBox @bind-Value="@_deptViewModel.FromDept.CDEPT_CODE" />
        </R_ItemLayout>
        <R_Lookup R_Before_Open_Lookup="BeforeOpenLookup" R_After_Open_Lookup="AfterOpenLookup"></R_Lookup>
        <R_ItemLayout col="6">
            <R_TextBox @bind-Value="@_deptViewModel.FromDept.CDEPT_NAME" Enabled="false" />
        </R_ItemLayout>
    </R_StackLayout>


    <R_StackLayout Row Class="justify-content-end">
        <R_ItemLayout>
            <R_Button OnClick="Button_OnClickProcessAsync">
                @_localizer["BTN_PROCESS"]
            </R_Button>
        </R_ItemLayout>
        <R_ItemLayout>
            <R_Button OnClick="Button_OnClickCloseAsync">
                @_localizer["BTN_CANCEL"]
            </R_Button>
        </R_ItemLayout>
    </R_StackLayout>
</R_StackLayout>
